## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="22208-484">下面的示例演示如何使用此属性来指定在通过使用 HTTP 301 响应代码对永久重定向进行编码时的重定向 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22208-484">The following example shows how to use this property to specify the redirect URL when you code a permanent redirect by using the HTTP 301 response code.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
Response.StatusCode = 301;  
Response.Status = "301 Moved Permanently";  
Response.RedirectLocation = "http://www.newurl.com ";  
Response.End();  
```
